{"tid":1691503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有暴力潔癖嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-03T16:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T16:33:07.000Z","uid":81909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6590b02939ec8b629e44fe4e7d95177a2ea0a443","tid":1691503,"uid":81909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"唔係要屌你地 <br />\n<br />\n一朝留意到有種心態 就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">&ldquo;黑警克制 我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔應該主動岀手</span>&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n呢句說話放係6 7月仲叫用得著<br />\n<br />\n但去到今日 呢五個月我地手足有幾多個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被虐打被強姦被自殺 </span></strong></span>已經係難以估計 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論我地點私了 都肯撚定唔會暴力得過班黑曱甴同藍絲對我地嘅暴力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當你見到手足做野會有少少少少反對<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>望下堆相 同我save低佢 提醒下自己有幾多仇係未報 </ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rYdKAKz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrYdKAKz.png&h=632f4377&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZTKAKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZTKAKA.jpg&h=b8413fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZVhbhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZVhbhW.png&h=f696d469&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYXzdwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYXzdwh.jpg&h=a5b65ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZynnpC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZynnpC.jpg&h=e61d743c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ME4edwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FME4edwi.jpg&h=b699974d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXa5kbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt